, holotype, male, external appearance, dorsal view (1); external appearance, lateral view (2); left antenna (3); left anterior tarsus (4); tibia and tarsus of left anterior leg, dorsal view (5); tibia and tarsus of left anterior leg, lateral view (6); left leg, dorsal view (7); left leg, ventral view (8); pygidium (9); ultimate abdominal ventrite (10); aedeagus, dorsal view (11); tegmen (12); distribution map (13). Scale bar 0.5 mm.
