<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,619,645]" pageId="5" pageNumber="381">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is named after Dr Nikita E. Vikhrev (Zoological Museum of 
<collectingRegion box="[1148,1307,619,645]" country="Russia" name="Moscow" pageId="5" pageNumber="381">Moscow State</collectingRegion>
